### RescueGuide API - InstructionStep Controller Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5238/api/instructionstep

### Get all instruction steps
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get instruction step by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Get instruction step by ID (non-existent)
GET {{baseUrl}}/999

### Create new instruction step
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 7,
  "instructionCategoryId": 1,
  "instructionCategory": null,
  "order": 1,
  "title": "Neuer Schritt",
  "description": "Beschreibung des neuen Schritts",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

### Create another instruction step
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 8,
  "instructionCategoryId": 1,
  "instructionCategory": null,
  "order": 2,
  "title": "Zweiter Schritt",
  "description": "Beschreibung des zweiten Schritts",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image2.jpg"
}

### Update instruction step
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "instructionCategoryId": 1,
  "instructionCategory": null,
  "order": 1,
  "title": "Aktualisierter Schritt",
  "description": "Aktualisierte Beschreibung",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/updated-image.jpg"
}

### Delete instruction step
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1

### Delete non-existent instruction step
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/999

### Update non-existent instruction step
PUT {{baseUrl}}/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 999,
  "instructionCategoryId": 1,
  "instructionCategory": null,
  "order": 1,
  "title": "Test",
  "description": "Test Description",
  "imageUrl": null
}

